title: Sumalatha Ambareesh salutes PSI Jagadish
text:
Bengaluru woke up to sad news today. PSI Jagadish, attached to the Doddaballapur police was stabbed to death by burglars in Nelamangala. Everyone has been saluting the brave Police Sub Inspector, and one among them is Sumalatha Ambareesh.
The veteran actress took to her Twitter page to salute the "real life hero" and gave her condolences to the family. Her tweet read, "A real life hero..salutes galore...and heartfelt condolences to everyone who lost him."
